data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous gem in vibrant Windsor Park! Every inch of this home has been meticulously crafted for modern living. Enjoy the perfect fusion of aesthetics & convenience that sets this property apart. The main suite is a true sanctuary with separate tub & shower, & walk-in closet. Fully fenced backyard is a private retreat, complete with a charming back porch, ideal for al fresco dining with friends and family. Walking distance to the hottest spots in town: Amelia's, Kan Kan Cinema, Spades Park Public Library & Spades Park, home of Feast of Lanterns Festival in August. In 5 min, you'll find yourself in the heart of Bottleworks & Mass Ave. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own your slice of urban paradise in Windsor Park.
